abstract: Indonesia's Supreme Court rejected an appeal by a Polish tourist who was convicted of treason after meeting with Papuan independence supporters and instead increased his prison term, a lawyer said Wednesday.
snippet: Indonesia's Supreme Court rejected an appeal by a Polish tourist who was convicted of treason after meeting with Papuan independence supporters and instead increased his prison term, a lawyer said Wednesday.
lead_paragraph: JAKARTA, Indonesia — Indonesia's Supreme Court rejected an appeal by a Polish tourist who was convicted of treason after meeting with Papuan independence supporters and instead increased his prison term, a lawyer said Wednesday.
headline_main: Indonesia Court Increases Jail Term for Polish Tourist
headline_print_headline: Indonesia Court Increases Jail Term for Polish Tourist

abstract: The Trump administration, eager to show progress on prescription drug costs, on Wednesday moved forward with its plan to allow Americans to safely and legally get access to lower-priced medicines from abroad.
snippet: The Trump administration, eager to show progress on prescription drug costs, on Wednesday moved forward with its plan to allow Americans to safely and legally get access to lower-priced medicines from abroad.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The Trump administration, eager to show progress on prescription drug costs, on Wednesday moved forward with its plan to allow Americans to safely and legally get access to lower-priced medicines from abroad.
headline_main: Plan to Import Cheaper Canadian Drugs Advances Under Trump
headline_print_headline: Plan to Import Cheaper Canadian Drugs Advances Under Trump

abstract: The proposal is still a long way from being finalized, and many expensive drugs, like insulin, would be excluded from state plans.
snippet: The proposal is still a long way from being finalized, and many expensive drugs, like insulin, would be excluded from state plans.
lead_paragraph: The Trump administration said on Wednesday that it would move forward with plans to allow states to safely import prescription drugs from Canada, for the first time.

abstract: German Chancellor Angela Merkel said on Wednesday that she favoured expanding the system of carbon emissions trading at EU level.
snippet: German Chancellor Angela Merkel said on Wednesday that she favoured expanding the system of carbon emissions trading at EU level.
lead_paragraph: BERLIN — German Chancellor Angela Merkel said on Wednesday that she favoured expanding the system of carbon emissions trading at EU level.
headline_main: Merkel Favours Expanding Emissions Trading at EU Level
headline_print_headline: Merkel Favours Expanding Emissions Trading at EU Level

abstract: Barcelona's record-breaking teenage sensation Ansu Fati has the ability and character to make an impact against Real Madrid in Wednesday's 'Clasico' at the Camp Nou, says club great Carles Puyol.
snippet: Barcelona's record-breaking teenage sensation Ansu Fati has the ability and character to make an impact against Real Madrid in Wednesday's 'Clasico' at the Camp Nou, says club great Carles Puyol.
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - Barcelona's record-breaking teenage sensation Ansu Fati has the ability and character to make an impact against Real Madrid in Wednesday's 'Clasico' at the Camp Nou, says club great Carles Puyol.
headline_main: Teenager Fati Ready to Make a Difference in 'Clasico', Says Puyol
headline_print_headline: Teenager Fati Ready to Make a Difference in 'Clasico', Says Puyol

abstract: Ridouan Taghi, 41, is accused of being involved in multiple killings and of heading a criminal gang that smuggles drugs.
snippet: Ridouan Taghi, 41, is accused of being involved in multiple killings and of heading a criminal gang that smuggles drugs.
lead_paragraph: The Netherlands’ most wanted man, described by the authorities as the kingpin atop a large and lethal criminal organization, is so elusive that he has never been convicted of a major crime. In fact, the authorities were long unsure of where he was.

abstract: Trailblazing feminist judge Brenda Hale used her valedictory speech as president of the UK Supreme Court on Wednesday to call for the judiciary to remain free from U.S.-style political influence and to poke fun at enduring sexism in the legal world.
snippet: Trailblazing feminist judge Brenda Hale used her valedictory speech as president of the UK Supreme Court on Wednesday to call for the judiciary to remain free from U.S.-style political influence and to poke fun at enduring sexism in the legal worl...
lead_paragraph: LONDON — Trailblazing feminist judge Brenda Hale used her valedictory speech as president of the UK Supreme Court on Wednesday to call for the judiciary to remain free from U.S.-style political influence and to poke fun at enduring sexism in the legal world.
headline_main: UK Supreme Court's 'Swashbuckling' Chief Hale Aims Parting Shots at Sexists, Politics
